node.text:
💬 "After coming fourth on Sunday, expectations are high now for Monza. This is very much a second home race for me now because I live just 15 kilometres from the track. The weekend will be something new for me, returning to a race circuit where I was the last person to win the Grand Prix. It will be something quite special, reminding me of some really unforgettable moments from last season" 

Check out @pierregasly's full preview in the link in our bio! 👆 

#AlphaTauri #F1 #RedBull #Honda #Formula1⁣⁣⁣ #ItalianGP #PierreGasly
